---
---

<section class="historia section" id="historia">
  <div class="historia-bg-shapes">
    <div class="historia-orb historia-orb--1"></div>
    <div class="historia-orb historia-orb--2"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title" data-reveal>
      <span data-es="Nuestra" data-en="Our">Nuestra</span>
      <span class="accent" data-es="Historia" data-en="Story"> Historia</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="historia-text" data-reveal
       data-es="Fundada en San Juan Cacahuatepec, la familia Galindo trajo su conocimiento de la naturaleza a Puerto Escondido en los 80s para deleitarnos con estos exquisitos sabores."
       data-en="Founded in San Juan Cacahuatepec, the Galindo family brought their knowledge of nature to Puerto Escondido in the 80s to delight us with these exquisite flavors.">
      Fundada en San Juan Cacahuatepec, la familia Galindo trajo su conocimiento de la naturaleza a Puerto Escondido en los 80s para deleitarnos con estos exquisitos sabores.
    </p>

    <div class="historia-timeline">
      <div class="timeline-line"></div>

      <div class="timeline-item" data-reveal="left">
        <div class="timeline-icon">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-mountain-sun"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card glass">
          <h3 data-es="Los Orígenes" data-en="The Origins">Los Orígenes</h3>
          <p data-es="San Juan Cacahuatepec — donde la familia Galindo aprendió a trabajar con las frutas de la sierra oaxaqueña."
             data-en="San Juan Cacahuatepec — where the Galindo family learned to work with the fruits of the Oaxacan highlands.">
            San Juan Cacahuatepec — donde la familia Galindo aprendió a trabajar con las frutas de la sierra oaxaqueña.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
        <div class="timeline-icon">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-umbrella-beach"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card glass">
          <h3 data-es="Llegada a la Costa" data-en="Arrival at the Coast">Llegada a la Costa</h3>
          <p data-es="En los años 80, la familia trajo su arte a Puerto Escondido, instalándose frente al mar en Playa Zicatela."
             data-en="In the 80s, the family brought their craft to Puerto Escondido, setting up by the sea at Playa Zicatela.">
            En los años 80, la familia trajo su arte a Puerto Escondido, instalándose frente al mar en Playa Zicatela.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item" data-reveal="right">
        <div class="timeline-icon">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-ice-cream"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-card glass">
          <h3 data-es="Tres Generaciones" data-en="Three Generations">Tres Generaciones</h3>
          <p data-es="Hoy, tres generaciones mantienen viva la tradición de la nieve de garrafa artesanal con frutas naturales."
             data-en="Today, three generations keep alive the tradition of artisanal barrel-churned ice cream with natural fruits.">
            Hoy, tres generaciones mantienen viva la tradición de la nieve de garrafa artesanal con frutas naturales.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .historia {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-cool) 50%, var(--bg-section-alt) 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .historia-bg-shapes {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .historia-orb {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(100px);
  }

  .historia-orb--1 {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: rgba(157, 249, 255, 0.1);
    top: -50px;
    right: -100px;
    animation: pulse-glow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .historia-orb--2 {
    width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    background: rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.06);
    bottom: -50px;
    left: -80px;
    animation: pulse-glow 8s ease-in-out infinite 4s;
  }

  .historia .section-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .historia-text {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 1rem auto 3.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .historia-timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-line {
    position: absolute;
    left: 28px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--cyan), var(--magenta), var(--cyan));
    opacity: 0.3;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 58px;
    height: 58px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--magenta), var(--cyan));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--magenta-glow), 0 4px 15px var(--cyan-glow);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-spring);
  }

  .timeline-item:hover .timeline-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .timeline-card {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    transition: transform 0.3s var(--ease-smooth),
                box-shadow 0.3s var(--ease-smooth),
                border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .timeline-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(157, 249, 255, 0.12),
                0 0 30px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .timeline-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-line {
      left: 22px;
    }

    .timeline-icon {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .timeline-card {
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
  }
</style>
